台巴打殺出重圍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n燈力係燒山沈大師之上 有過之而無不及 <br />\n戰績 <br />\n春袋開榴槤 數未找 <br />\n貼丁圖自爆 數未找<br />\n侵侵都要麵仔頭 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"878572bd4653d081ef54d2f9cc5dd2e6daed15f2","tid":1727544,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:14:33.000Z","msg":"****眾籌****<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，仲係要借個位&amp;<span style=\"color: red;\">因5 毛post 不幫你推POST<br />\n</span><br />\n鍾庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港性民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 (eg. 721, 831) &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，然後做份國際文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 話比全世界聽：5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n(<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌到而家先64%</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 仲要大家支持)<br />\n<br />\n第五期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1</a> <span style=\"color: red;\">(new)</span><br />\n第三&amp;四期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1</a><br />\n第二期民調結果POST <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054</a><br />\n第一期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌link:  <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQIE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=22c84a4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a><br />\n官方link (我們香港人計劃) :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2F&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQIE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=6cdc9fdf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n(對唔住，咁危難時刻下我知而家仲叫大家課金可能好反感，但我相信兄弟爬山，各有各做，行得通就全力去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"e1c56d8d52f1d7b7d063475f33ce709ffb108747","tid":1727544,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:14:55.000Z","msg":"無贏到 只係打到對手又出多張新牌"},{"pid":"762fd35e3531bbf300782e3ad8c5b1581bda0c52","tid":1727544,"uid":191588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:17:07.000Z","msg":"啱<br />\n香港人堅持"},{"pid":"74b21318b68faa47a2d6e748e3ccd2bbfa9cc4ec","tid":1727544,"uid":81150,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8abcd010730b2814126077da0bd6eb9d8a6ee6bc","tid":1727544,"uid":103759,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:13:46.000Z","msg":"麵仔係咪第一次係時事台開post? <br />\n<br />\n為大家介紹返 <br />\n麵媽咪 原名媽咪麵 <br />\n為財經台台主 多次帶領財經台巴打殺出重圍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n燈力係燒山沈大師之上 有過之而無不及 <br />\n戰績 <br />\n春袋開榴槤 數未找 <br />\n貼丁圖自爆 數未找<br />\n侵侵都要麵仔頭 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:17:11.000Z","msg":"準備係時事台插旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9a6d4c74152e20ff6e56987cc861c2e5a17a665","tid":1727544,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74b21318b68faa47a2d6e748e3ccd2bbfa9cc4ec","tid":1727544,"uid":81150,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8abcd010730b2814126077da0bd6eb9d8a6ee6bc","tid":1727544,"uid":103759,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:13:46.000Z","msg":"麵仔係